  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.mp4?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄  <strong>Gnomdom </strong>is a point and click puzzle game where you find little gnomes stuck in various places and help them return to their home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help the gnomes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄  Dive into a captivating world with hand-drawn visuals that breathe life into every frame. Explore a charming universe where artistry meets gameplay in a mesmerizing style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging and relaxing puzzles </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming illustration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Nature environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmospheric nature sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Funny and relaxing levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who are we?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We're a two-person team with passion and determination. We're crafting our debut game, pouring everything we've got into it. Despite our size, we're driven by creativity and innovation, ready to make our mark in the indie world.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.mp4?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄  <strong>Gnomdom </strong>is a point and click puzzle game where you find little gnomes stuck in various places and help them return to their home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help the gnomes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄  Dive into a captivating world with hand-drawn visuals that breathe life into every frame. Explore a charming universe where artistry meets gameplay in a mesmerizing style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging and relaxing puzzles </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming illustration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Nature environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmospheric nature sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Funny and relaxing levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who are we?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We're a two-person team with passion and determination. We're crafting our debut game, pouring everything we've got into it. Despite our size, we're driven by creativity and innovation, ready to make our mark in the indie world.</p>",
